      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add your<strong> hot dog sausage[s]</strong> to one side of a<strong> tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 25 min or until the sausage is cooked through</p>",
