    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the sausages are cooking, slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong> as thinly as you can</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong> to a small bowl with your <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled shallot</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
