    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> panko breadcrumbs</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and a small pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Cook for 6-8 min or until golden, stirring frequently – this is your <strong>garlic breadcrumbs</strong></p>",
