    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Once the sauce has thickened, add the <strong>cooked macaroni </strong>and <strong>grated cheese</strong> to the pot with a generous grind of <strong>pepper</strong> and a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up until fully coated and the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>macaroni cheese</strong></p><p>Once the sausages have had 25 min, add your <strong>hot dog bun[s] </strong>to the other side of the baking tray[s] and cook for 3 min or until warmed through</p>",
