    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut a slit into the top of your<strong> hot dog bun[s]</strong></p><p>Fill each<strong> hot dog bun </strong>with a <strong>hot dog sausage</strong>, then top with some of the <strong>macaroni cheese</strong>, your <strong>BBQ sauce </strong>and some of the <strong>garlic breadcrumbs</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> remaining macaroni cheese </strong>topped with the <strong>remaining garlic breadcrumbs </strong>and the <strong>tomato & shallot</strong> <strong>salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
